  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bullet
    The bullets that are flying through the game.
    Combatant
    An abstract class that has methods shared by both you and your opponent.
    DirectionalGameObjects
    An abstract class for all the objects that has an orientation in a direction.
    Gameboard
    The current state of the game board along with information about game state.
    GameObjects
    The game objects that exist on the game board.
    Opponent
    A representation of your opponent on the game board.
    Player
    A representation of your player on the game board.
    PowerUp
    The power ups on the map.
    Turret
    The turrets in the game.
    Wall
    The walls in the game.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Direction
    The different orientations of direction some objects can be.
    Move
    The different possible moves a player can make per turn.
    PowerUpType

    ProjectileTypes
    The two different types of projectiles in the game, bullet and laser.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    MapOutOfBoundsException
    The exception that is thrown when trying to retrieve an item on outside of the gameboard boundaries.
    NoItemException
    The exception that is thrown when trying to retrieve an item on the game board that doesn't exist.
